title: Grasping Tail
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

When a Malanthrope is fighting in a challenge, its opponent is reduced to half their normal number of attacks (rounded down) and Initiative 1 for the duration of the challenge. Glorious Intervention cancels this ability.